stylometry: In this situation, we want to minimize cost and maximize profit, how much should we produce, and how do we keep the demand coming. We want to find the best possible solution for a company like Ikea who believes in shipping everything flat.  They sell home furnishings towards the younger generations of new and upcoming families.  Everything they sell and ship is all in pieces for ready-to-assemble work.  When they ship their products they want everything to be as flat as possible.  By doing this they are drastically minimizing their shipping costs and maximizing their profits from the consumer.
